item.title: Visualising Australian Super Performance with F#
item.description: Australian Super Performance graphs are available on their website, but just as a simple exercise, lets replicate their graph, using FSharp.Charting. Graph generated from Australian Super Website Below is a screenshot of the associated cumulative % change for the period, for the investments shown in the graph above: First create a paket dependencies file: paket.dependencies source https://nuget.org/api/v2 nuget FSharp.Data nuget FSharp.Charting Run the following command to generate an include script, so you only need to include 1 file, rather than all dependencies.
